<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180419/f5b3853ab9aa440693dd8271506bf224.jpg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">在一切沉默之物中，墙与人的关系最为特殊，无墙，则无家</span></img></p>
